reviewText: I don't know what is up with the Jay Jay the jet plane Dvds from Amazon. Even the ones you get that are brand new and shrink wrapped, the DVD inside, the graphics on the disc itself are black and white, like the DVD is bootlegged. I have bought these Dvds before brand new and the graphics on the outside of the disc were in color. So I don't know what is going on.
arrived quickly and was reasonably priced.  Has been watched and enjoyed several times since.  thank You Seller
